{"type": "article", "id": 17110, "title": "铜环吊坠", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-05T10:11:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160209Ux71twjdiSqMcp5E.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是台湾文具品牌永日文创联合文林堂设计的铜环吊坠，方形圆孔，在铜环一边凸起一个铅字“好”，以寄托美好的愿望。吊坠可以从中间拆成两片，将这个铅字替换成别的文字，有点像活字印刷 ，是结合传统文化和现代设计的范例。此外，吊坠的包装也很有意思，将说明文字卷起来套在铜环里面，铜环充当了一个束带，有古雅的韵味。<a href=\"http://www.in-photoart.com/newsite/customers/ordergroup_detail.php?level0_id=1&amp;level1_id=11&amp;p_id=6160&amp;stype=\" target=\"_blank\">这里购买链接。 </a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144302Jf7m53UAinIQYE4q.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261443030hTpguvJZlwAsWQi.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144304fzYpM2WFJyxSPUjw.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"487\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74923077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144304CFcnJlOeSTRwXabL.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"975\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}